1
00:01:20,960 --> 00:01:26,720
[A Splendid Match]

2
00:01:27,380 --> 00:01:29,720
[Episode 17]

3
00:01:40,350 --> 00:01:41,210
Your Highness.

4
00:01:42,070 --> 00:01:42,870
Where is my father?

5
00:01:42,870 --> 00:01:43,870
The Marquis went to the military camp.

6
00:01:43,870 --> 00:01:44,430
What?

7
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:47,120
Did he say when he'd be back?

8
00:01:47,120 --> 00:01:48,450
The Marquis didn't say.

9
00:01:50,070 --> 00:01:50,600
Let's go.

10
00:01:54,920 --> 00:01:55,430
Hurry.

11
00:01:55,789 --> 00:01:56,400
Don't let anyone know.

12
00:01:56,400 --> 00:01:56,759
Yes.

13
00:01:57,000 --> 00:01:57,560
Hold on.

14
00:01:57,440 --> 00:02:01,320
[A Legacy of Virtue and Grace]

15
00:02:11,150 --> 00:02:12,030
Let me ask you.

16
00:02:12,590 --> 00:02:13,430
Did you go again

17
00:02:13,430 --> 00:02:14,710
to see that Gu Jinzhao?

18
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:18,400
How did you know, Mother?

19
00:02:29,150 --> 00:02:30,750
So you had someone following me

20
00:02:30,750 --> 00:02:32,150
these past few days?

21
00:02:32,870 --> 00:02:34,590
If I didn't send someone to follow you,

22
00:02:34,590 --> 00:02:35,190
who knows

23
00:02:35,210 --> 00:02:36,260
what you would do.

24
00:02:37,030 --> 00:02:39,280
I wanted to talk to you
about this earlier,

25
00:02:39,280 --> 00:02:40,680
but your sister stopped me,

26
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:42,190
saying she would talk to you.

27
00:02:42,190 --> 00:02:43,030
But what happened?

28
00:02:43,030 --> 00:02:44,430
You didn't listen at all.

29
00:02:46,370 --> 00:02:47,560
You brazenly

30
00:02:47,560 --> 00:02:49,160
went to a young lady's house.

31
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:50,560
That eldest Miss Gu

32
00:02:51,079 --> 00:02:52,360
really lacks manners.

33
00:02:52,960 --> 00:02:54,840
She actually let you into her manor.

34
00:02:54,840 --> 00:02:56,590
The family discipline of the Gu Manor

35
00:02:56,590 --> 00:02:57,710
is evident.

36
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:00,220
Let me tell you,

37
00:03:01,190 --> 00:03:03,240
you are not allowed to see her again.

38
00:03:03,870 --> 00:03:05,000
From today onwards,

39
00:03:05,360 --> 00:03:06,410
you will obediently

40
00:03:06,410 --> 00:03:07,470
copy books at home.

41
00:03:07,630 --> 00:03:08,960
Without my permission,

42
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:10,890
you are not allowed to go anywhere.

43
00:03:14,100 --> 00:03:14,840
That's fine.

44
00:03:16,060 --> 00:03:18,520
I wanted to practice
my handwriting anyway.

45
00:03:18,630 --> 00:03:19,360
Li Xianhuai,

46
00:03:20,240 --> 00:03:21,150
go find me some

47
00:03:21,150 --> 00:03:22,410
excellent copybooks.

48
00:03:23,360 --> 00:03:23,750
Yes.

49
00:03:28,470 --> 00:03:29,280
Mr. Xiao.

50
00:03:30,630 --> 00:03:31,190
Madam.

51
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:34,200
The Marquis went to the main camp today.

52
00:03:34,240 --> 00:03:35,960
There are many affairs in the manor.

53
00:03:35,960 --> 00:03:36,560
I have no way

54
00:03:36,560 --> 00:03:37,960
to keep a close eye on him.

55
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:39,630
You are Xian's master.

56
00:03:40,079 --> 00:03:41,190
I will have to trouble you

57
00:03:41,190 --> 00:03:42,320
to keep an eye on him.

58
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:44,960
Yes, Madam.

59
00:03:52,430 --> 00:03:55,710
[Marquis Changxing's Mansion]

60
00:04:09,180 --> 00:04:10,510
That's the death knell.

61
00:04:12,150 --> 00:04:13,880
Could it be that His Majesty...

62
00:04:26,130 --> 00:04:27,980
The moment has finally come.

63
00:04:29,200 --> 00:04:31,390
In the autumn of
the 35th year of Jingning,

64
00:04:31,390 --> 00:04:33,730
His Majesty passed away.

65
00:04:33,920 --> 00:04:35,040
From the palace to the common folk,

66
00:04:35,040 --> 00:04:36,920
the entire nation shall observe mourning.

67
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:37,750
From today on,

68
00:04:38,240 --> 00:04:40,040
the capital is under
curfew and martial law.

69
00:04:40,040 --> 00:04:42,240
Strict checks will be
carried out at all city gates.

70
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:44,040
No entry or exit without orders.

71
00:04:49,300 --> 00:04:50,490
His Majesty has passed away.

72
00:04:50,490 --> 00:04:51,750
I need to enter the palace.

73
00:04:51,750 --> 00:04:53,200
Madam has already entered the palace.

74
00:04:53,200 --> 00:04:54,710
Before leaving, she specially instructed

75
00:04:54,710 --> 00:04:56,270
that she asked for sick leave for you.

76
00:04:56,270 --> 00:04:57,680
Please stay in the mansion.

77
00:04:57,680 --> 00:04:58,409
Do not leave.

78
00:05:01,670 --> 00:05:03,710
Our household must keep
a low profile these next few days.

79
00:05:02,270 --> 00:05:03,510
[Blessings Passed Down for Generations]

80
00:05:03,800 --> 00:05:05,360
Purchasing will change from once a day

81
00:05:05,360 --> 00:05:06,630
to once every three days.

82
00:05:06,630 --> 00:05:08,030
If anyone needs to go out,

83
00:05:08,430 --> 00:05:09,920
come to me to get a token.

84
00:05:10,510 --> 00:05:11,480
Without a token,

85
00:05:11,870 --> 00:05:14,470
no one is allowed to
go out without permission.

86
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:15,390
Yes.

87
00:05:16,310 --> 00:05:17,800
My Lady, Guard Li is here.

88
00:05:19,680 --> 00:05:20,310
Miss Gu.

89
00:05:20,680 --> 00:05:21,580
Madam has gone to the palace.

90
00:05:21,580 --> 00:05:22,750
His Highness is afraid
of alerting Xiao You

91
00:05:22,750 --> 00:05:24,010
and doesn't dare to force his way out.

92
00:05:24,010 --> 00:05:26,070
We have to rely on you to think of a way.

93
00:05:27,360 --> 00:05:28,310
The Third Master

94
00:05:28,720 --> 00:05:30,920
has probably entered the palace by now.

95
00:05:38,270 --> 00:05:39,390
As you expected,

96
00:05:39,420 --> 00:05:40,750
the Shenji Battalion has indeed

97
00:05:40,750 --> 00:05:42,159
been making unusual moves
these past few days.

98
00:05:42,159 --> 00:05:43,750
Not only have they
been drilling repeatedly,

99
00:05:43,750 --> 00:05:44,750
but yesterday the Ministry of War

100
00:05:44,750 --> 00:05:45,560
also transported inside

101
00:05:45,560 --> 00:05:47,159
ten full carts of gunpowder.

102
00:05:47,920 --> 00:05:48,980
Then it all adds up.

103
00:05:50,870 --> 00:05:52,040
On the surface,

104
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:54,190
Prince Ruichang is planning a rebellion,

105
00:05:54,190 --> 00:05:55,040
but in reality,

106
00:05:55,040 --> 00:05:57,330
my mentor is intentionally indulging him.

107
00:05:57,330 --> 00:05:58,860
He is using Prince Ruichang

108
00:05:58,920 --> 00:06:00,810
to drag Marquis Changxing into this.

109
00:06:00,810 --> 00:06:02,440
So you mean...

110
00:06:05,430 --> 00:06:07,760
Prince Ruichang is planning a rebellion.

111
00:06:08,070 --> 00:06:09,750
His only chance is

112
00:06:10,120 --> 00:06:12,140
the moment His Majesty passes away.

113
00:06:12,270 --> 00:06:14,470
With just the few mansion guards he has,

114
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:16,120
to start a rebellion,

115
00:06:16,120 --> 00:06:17,780
he can only do it in the palace.

116
00:06:18,340 --> 00:06:19,430
Once he makes a move,

117
00:06:19,430 --> 00:06:20,490
Marquis Changxing

118
00:06:20,630 --> 00:06:22,120
will definitely enter the palace

119
00:06:22,120 --> 00:06:24,920
to protect the Emperor
and suppress the rebellion.

120
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:26,390
But between these two sides,

121
00:06:26,390 --> 00:06:27,650
whoever wins in the end

122
00:06:28,630 --> 00:06:29,510
could never be

123
00:06:29,510 --> 00:06:31,370
a match for the Shenji Battalion.

124
00:06:50,370 --> 00:06:51,050
Mentor.

125
00:06:54,430 --> 00:06:56,000
Your only task today

126
00:06:56,050 --> 00:06:57,720
is to protect the Crown Prince.

127
00:06:57,720 --> 00:06:59,159
Even if you die,

128
00:06:59,870 --> 00:07:01,870
you must keep the Crown Prince safe.

129
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:02,820
I

130
00:07:03,000 --> 00:07:04,260
guarantee with my life

131
00:07:04,270 --> 00:07:05,870
to protect the Crown Prince.

132
00:07:06,190 --> 00:07:07,390
Besides, Mentor, you have

133
00:07:07,390 --> 00:07:09,050
already made a thorough plan.

134
00:07:09,560 --> 00:07:10,490
The Crown Prince

135
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:12,320
will definitely be fine.

136
00:07:13,270 --> 00:07:14,390
His Majesty has passed away.

137
00:07:14,390 --> 00:07:16,360
The Crown Prince will mourn at the bier.

138
00:07:16,360 --> 00:07:17,360
Prince Ruichang

139
00:07:17,430 --> 00:07:18,630
must also be present.

140
00:07:19,510 --> 00:07:21,240
We cannot afford any mistakes.

141
00:07:21,680 --> 00:07:22,240
Yes.

142
00:07:24,190 --> 00:07:24,800
Mentor.

143
00:07:25,830 --> 00:07:27,310
What about Marquis Changxing?

144
00:07:27,310 --> 00:07:29,240
You don't need to worry about that.

145
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:31,830
The Shenji Battalion will take them down

146
00:07:31,830 --> 00:07:33,630
and confirm their treason.

147
00:07:40,200 --> 00:07:43,770
[The Reform of Land and Taxation]

148
00:07:45,480 --> 00:07:46,070
That day,

149
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:49,950
when my mentor wrote
this The Reform of Land and Taxation,

150
00:07:49,950 --> 00:07:50,830
I just felt

151
00:07:51,310 --> 00:07:52,970
a surge of emotion in my chest.

152
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:55,400
If Great Yan is to become
strong and reform,

153
00:07:56,000 --> 00:07:57,680
it must have someone like my mentor,

154
00:07:57,680 --> 00:07:59,510
with great wisdom and courage,

155
00:07:59,510 --> 00:08:00,920
to manage and direct.

156
00:08:01,720 --> 00:08:02,780
But what about now?

157
00:08:05,430 --> 00:08:07,800
Maritime transport is indeed profitable.

158
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:09,270
But to develop it,

159
00:08:09,270 --> 00:08:11,190
deliberately leaving
the river embankments unrepaired,

160
00:08:11,190 --> 00:08:12,630
is this for the court and the people,

161
00:08:12,630 --> 00:08:14,160
or for partisan struggles?

162
00:08:16,370 --> 00:08:22,690
[Immersed in the Classics and History]

163
00:08:16,680 --> 00:08:17,940
Marquis Changxing...

164
00:08:18,270 --> 00:08:18,870
Marquis Changxing

165
00:08:18,870 --> 00:08:20,800
indeed opposes the new tax policy.

166
00:08:21,240 --> 00:08:22,920
But to ignore the risks of war,

167
00:08:23,270 --> 00:08:25,270
doing everything to bring him down,

168
00:08:25,680 --> 00:08:27,320
is this for the sake of the country,

169
00:08:27,320 --> 00:08:29,510
or for personal gain?

170
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:38,400
Third Master,

171
00:08:39,320 --> 00:08:40,270
hold on.

172
00:08:41,669 --> 00:08:44,400
Even if Marquis Changxing
has countless faults,

173
00:08:44,720 --> 00:08:45,320
just the fact

174
00:08:45,320 --> 00:08:47,240
that he can deter the barbarians

175
00:08:47,960 --> 00:08:49,720
is enough for me

176
00:08:49,740 --> 00:08:51,270
to protect him with my life.

177
00:08:56,060 --> 00:09:02,220
[Immersed in the Classics and History]

178
00:08:59,000 --> 00:08:59,750
Otherwise,

179
00:09:00,590 --> 00:09:02,650
if war breaks out at the border again,

180
00:09:02,670 --> 00:09:03,800
how can we talk about

181
00:09:03,840 --> 00:09:05,390
maritime transport and river repairs?

182
00:09:05,390 --> 00:09:08,360
Equalized land and lower taxes
will be nothing but empty promises.

183
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:09,510
Third Master.

184
00:09:10,840 --> 00:09:12,870
This is a dead end.

185
00:09:13,760 --> 00:09:16,020
Prince Ruichang will inevitably rebel.

186
00:09:16,240 --> 00:09:18,600
Marquis Changxing will also
surely quell the rebellion.

187
00:09:18,600 --> 00:09:19,790
The Shenji Battalion

188
00:09:19,790 --> 00:09:21,920
is directly under the Ministry of War,

189
00:09:21,960 --> 00:09:23,890
obeying only the Grand Secretary.

190
00:09:24,750 --> 00:09:26,000
How can you save him?

191
00:09:27,950 --> 00:09:29,950
Even if you save Marquis Changxing,

192
00:09:30,720 --> 00:09:32,150
if the Grand Secretary finds out

193
00:09:32,150 --> 00:09:33,360
about your actions,

194
00:09:34,870 --> 00:09:36,550
everything will be over.

195
00:09:38,480 --> 00:09:41,280
I'm afraid you won't
even be able to save your life.

196
00:09:51,840 --> 00:09:53,360
So in this situation,

197
00:09:56,790 --> 00:09:59,190
not only must I protect Marquis Changxing,

198
00:10:00,320 --> 00:10:02,050
but I must also protect myself.

199
00:10:31,720 --> 00:10:32,380
Be careful.

200
00:10:33,200 --> 00:10:34,910
It's the Marquis's Black Armor Army.

201
00:10:34,910 --> 00:10:37,310
They seem to be
heading towards the palace.

202
00:10:38,870 --> 00:10:40,200
Let's hurry up.

203
00:10:40,960 --> 00:10:41,560
Hyah!

204
00:10:44,360 --> 00:10:44,840
Hyah!

205
00:10:47,960 --> 00:10:48,620
Fifth Aunt.

206
00:10:49,030 --> 00:10:49,760
Eldest Miss.

207
00:10:50,030 --> 00:10:51,200
In such chaotic times,

208
00:10:51,200 --> 00:10:52,130
why are you here?

209
00:10:53,350 --> 00:10:54,230
And you too?

210
00:10:54,440 --> 00:10:55,270
Eldest Miss,

211
00:10:55,510 --> 00:10:56,720
the Marquis went to the military camp.

212
00:10:56,720 --> 00:10:58,080
His Highness has been confined by Madam.

213
00:10:58,080 --> 00:10:59,200
He can't leave the mansion.

214
00:10:59,200 --> 00:11:00,600
I really had no other way,

215
00:11:00,600 --> 00:11:02,060
so I asked Miss Gu for help.

216
00:11:02,480 --> 00:11:04,510
My Lady! My Lady!

217
00:11:05,240 --> 00:11:05,670
My Lady.

218
00:11:05,670 --> 00:11:06,570
Hui.

219
00:11:06,840 --> 00:11:08,480
Hui had a bump while being changed.

220
00:11:08,480 --> 00:11:09,680
She's crying for you.

221
00:11:16,360 --> 00:11:17,360
Hui has a high fever.

222
00:11:17,360 --> 00:11:18,720
Quick, fetch a physician.

223
00:11:18,720 --> 00:11:19,440
Yes.

224
00:11:19,700 --> 00:11:20,360
It's fine.

225
00:11:20,360 --> 00:11:21,230
Go on.

226
00:11:21,510 --> 00:11:22,170
Fifth Aunt,

227
00:11:22,190 --> 00:11:23,600
do you know Young Master Ye's master,

228
00:11:23,600 --> 00:11:24,150
Xiao You?

229
00:11:24,320 --> 00:11:25,030
Of course.

230
00:11:25,550 --> 00:11:27,080
But his real name is Xiao Qishan.

231
00:11:27,080 --> 00:11:29,390
He was a strategist
for the late Prince Chengqing.

232
00:11:29,390 --> 00:11:30,520
How do you know that?

233
00:11:30,600 --> 00:11:31,840
The Ji family's business spans the world,

234
00:11:31,840 --> 00:11:33,480
so we naturally have our channels.

235
00:11:33,480 --> 00:11:34,960
This person is secretly colluding

236
00:11:34,960 --> 00:11:36,170
with Prince Ruichang.

237
00:11:36,170 --> 00:11:37,980
Prince Ruichang has always brooded over

238
00:11:37,980 --> 00:11:39,600
the death of Prince Chengqing.

239
00:11:39,600 --> 00:11:40,480
With His Majesty's passing,

240
00:11:40,480 --> 00:11:41,480
Prince Ruichang is very likely

241
00:11:41,480 --> 00:11:43,440
to start a rebellion
during the national mourning.

242
00:11:43,440 --> 00:11:44,890
If they succeed in their revolt,

243
00:11:44,890 --> 00:11:46,550
given their hatred for the Marquis,

244
00:11:46,550 --> 00:11:48,550
they definitely won't spare
Marquis Changxing's Mansion.

245
00:11:48,550 --> 00:11:49,690
But right now, only Young Master Ye

246
00:11:49,690 --> 00:11:50,770
has the token to enter the palace.

247
00:11:50,770 --> 00:11:51,840
We must ask Young Master Ye

248
00:11:51,840 --> 00:11:53,440
to quickly warn the Marquis.

249
00:11:53,550 --> 00:11:54,150
Remember,

250
00:11:54,600 --> 00:11:55,800
don't alert Xiao You.

251
00:11:59,120 --> 00:12:00,250
Hui has a high fever.

252
00:12:00,270 --> 00:12:01,440
The streets are full of soldiers.

253
00:12:01,440 --> 00:12:03,150
The physicians outside refuse to come out.

254
00:12:03,150 --> 00:12:03,840
My lady is

255
00:12:03,840 --> 00:12:04,720
so worried,

256
00:12:04,910 --> 00:12:06,140
that's why we came to invite you.

257
00:12:06,140 --> 00:12:07,090
No problem.

258
00:12:19,390 --> 00:12:20,050
Young Master,

259
00:12:20,050 --> 00:12:21,710
Miss Gu said the streets
are being cleared,

260
00:12:21,710 --> 00:12:23,030
and carriages are too slow.
Afraid we wouldn't make it,

261
00:12:23,030 --> 00:12:24,760
she had me bring her horse over.

262
00:12:25,970 --> 00:12:26,770
Young Master,

263
00:12:26,980 --> 00:12:28,240
hold the reins tightly.

264
00:12:28,240 --> 00:12:29,960
Miss Gu also asked me to tell you

265
00:12:29,960 --> 00:12:30,760
to be careful.

266
00:12:31,510 --> 00:12:31,920
Hyah!

267
00:12:35,320 --> 00:12:36,510
Kneel.

268
00:12:35,440 --> 00:12:39,200
[The Emperor Sets the Ultimate Principle]

269
00:12:39,040 --> 00:12:40,760
First bow.

270
00:12:42,840 --> 00:12:43,870
Rise.

271
00:12:45,000 --> 00:12:46,120
Stand.

272
00:12:58,480 --> 00:12:59,790
Kneel.

273
00:13:06,030 --> 00:13:07,670
Second bow.

274
00:13:09,630 --> 00:13:10,750
Rise.

275
00:13:12,600 --> 00:13:14,440
Third bow.

276
00:13:15,180 --> 00:13:19,340
[The Emperor Sets the Ultimate Principle]

277
00:13:16,910 --> 00:13:18,030
Your Majesty!

278
00:13:18,440 --> 00:13:19,440
Your Majesty!

279
00:13:20,240 --> 00:13:21,080
Ye Xian.

280
00:13:23,790 --> 00:13:24,650
Your Highness!

281
00:13:24,840 --> 00:13:25,700
Your Highness!

282
00:13:26,030 --> 00:13:27,890
Summon the Imperial Physicians!

283
00:13:28,030 --> 00:13:29,080
Take him to the side hall.

284
00:13:29,080 --> 00:13:29,880
Your Majesty!

285
00:13:30,720 --> 00:13:31,580
Your Highness!

286
00:13:31,600 --> 00:13:32,370
Your Majesty!

287
00:13:32,370 --> 00:13:33,250
Your Majesty!

288
00:13:33,840 --> 00:13:34,960
Your Majesty!

289
00:13:35,870 --> 00:13:37,240
Your Majesty!

290
00:13:41,320 --> 00:13:41,870
Mentor,

291
00:13:42,270 --> 00:13:43,630
I'll go check on the Crown Prince.

292
00:13:43,630 --> 00:13:45,120
The palace gates are heavily guarded.

293
00:13:45,120 --> 00:13:46,780
How did Young Master Ye get in?

294
00:13:48,390 --> 00:13:49,840
Just now in the Eastern Palace,

295
00:13:49,840 --> 00:13:51,390
His Highness the Crown Prince told me

296
00:13:51,390 --> 00:13:53,720
