with Young Master Ye.

297
00:13:53,720 --> 00:13:54,520
Your Majesty.

298
00:13:54,840 --> 00:13:55,480
Go.

299
00:13:56,120 --> 00:13:56,600
Yes.

300
00:14:08,650 --> 00:14:13,160
[Uphold Rites and Elucidate Doctrines]

301
00:14:10,960 --> 00:14:13,300
His Highness is young and weak after all.

302
00:14:13,750 --> 00:14:15,750
He didn't eat
a single grain for breakfast,

303
00:14:15,750 --> 00:14:17,240
with all this grief and exhaustion,

304
00:14:17,240 --> 00:14:18,480
he couldn't hold on.

305
00:14:18,670 --> 00:14:20,910
Then please write
a prescription, Director Wu.

306
00:14:20,910 --> 00:14:21,480
Yes.

307
00:14:25,190 --> 00:14:28,770
[Uphold Rites and Elucidate Doctrines]

308
00:14:33,150 --> 00:14:34,670
The late emperor has passed away.

309
00:14:34,670 --> 00:14:36,670
Your Highness must be heartbroken.

310
00:14:37,120 --> 00:14:37,670
However,

311
00:14:38,240 --> 00:14:41,570
Your Highness shoulders
the responsibility of the nation.

312
00:14:42,120 --> 00:14:43,440
Please, Your Highness,

313
00:14:43,440 --> 00:14:44,840
