314
00:14:45,270 --> 00:14:46,200
I understand.

315
00:14:48,030 --> 00:14:49,030
Everyone, leave.

316
00:14:49,630 --> 00:14:50,270
I

317
00:14:50,550 --> 00:14:52,080
