320
00:14:59,790 --> 00:15:01,360
Why should I listen to you?

321
00:15:02,720 --> 00:15:04,780
I will stay and protect His Highness.

322
00:15:07,670 --> 00:15:08,930
Then, Young Master Ye,

323
00:15:09,200 --> 00:15:11,330
you should definitely guard outside.

324
00:15:11,750 --> 00:15:12,950
If anything happens,

325
00:15:13,080 --> 00:15:15,010
you can charge to the front, right?

326
00:15:35,490 --> 00:15:38,710
[Uphold Rites and Elucidate Doctrines]

327
00:16:10,790 --> 00:16:12,080
Your Majesty!

328
00:16:13,550 --> 00:16:15,030
Your Majesty!

329
00:16:15,750 --> 00:16:16,500
There are rebels!

330
00:16:16,500 --> 00:16:17,740
Protect the Crown Prince!

331
00:16:17,410 --> 00:16:19,990
[The Emperor Sets the Ultimate Principle]

332
00:16:20,150 --> 00:16:21,150
Arrest them all!

333
00:16:33,660 --> 00:16:36,070
[The Emperor Sets the Ultimate Principle]

334
00:16:42,470 --> 00:16:43,700
Li Qi,

335
00:16:45,120 --> 00:16:47,320
