336
00:16:49,590 --> 00:16:53,800
[The Emperor Sets the Ultimate Principle]

337
00:16:52,120 --> 00:16:55,410
Your day has finally come!

338
00:17:00,080 --> 00:17:00,810
Ram the door!

339
00:17:04,980 --> 00:17:05,980
Pry the door open!

340
00:17:32,200 --> 00:17:33,550
Traitor!

341
00:17:34,090 --> 00:17:35,120
How impudent!

342
00:17:37,870 --> 00:17:39,660
Old fool.

343
00:17:40,540 --> 00:17:42,590
Are you tired of living?

344
00:17:43,400 --> 00:17:43,920
You...

345
00:17:49,150 --> 00:17:51,170
[The Emperor Sets the Ultimate Principle]

346
00:18:15,650 --> 00:18:16,640
[The Emperor Sets the Ultimate Principle]

347
00:18:19,250 --> 00:18:20,580
The Shenji Battalion.

348
00:18:33,200 --> 00:18:34,070
Ye Guangsheng!

349
00:18:34,590 --> 00:18:35,750
Taking advantage
of His Majesty's passing,

350
00:18:35,750 --> 00:18:36,740
you led troops into the palace

351
00:18:36,740 --> 00:18:37,960
with the intent to rebel.

352
00:18:37,960 --> 00:18:38,980
Do you plead guilty?

353
00:18:38,980 --> 00:18:40,880
I entered the palace
to protect His Majesty.

354
00:18:40,880 --> 00:18:42,000
You stopped me.

355
00:18:42,640 --> 00:18:44,100
What are your intentions?

356
00:18:45,640 --> 00:18:46,500
Fu Hailian.

357
00:18:47,830 --> 00:18:48,440
You...

358
00:18:48,920 --> 00:18:49,830
Li Zhi.

359
00:18:50,960 --> 00:18:52,210
Did you really think

360
00:18:52,550 --> 00:18:54,110
your childish attempt

361
00:18:54,880 --> 00:18:56,570
to usurp the throne

362
00:18:56,750 --> 00:18:57,960
would succeed?

363
00:19:00,430 --> 00:19:02,230
Before His Majesty passed away,

364
00:19:02,240 --> 00:19:03,970
you secretly gathered troops.

365
00:19:04,000 --> 00:19:05,680
Yet you claim you have
no intention of rebelling?

366
00:19:05,680 --> 00:19:06,510
Take him down!

367
00:19:12,470 --> 00:19:14,090
Protect the Marquis!

368
00:19:17,790 --> 00:19:18,590
Yun Tao.

369
00:19:18,960 --> 00:19:20,900
Order your men right now

370
00:19:21,240 --> 00:19:22,840
to surrender their weapons.

371
00:19:23,550 --> 00:19:24,350
I promise you

372
00:19:24,750 --> 00:19:26,880
I won't implicate your entire family.

373
00:19:31,550 --> 00:19:33,590
[The Emperor Sets the Ultimate Principle]

374
00:21:08,500 --> 00:21:09,430
Young Master Ye.

375
00:21:09,750 --> 00:21:11,800
As long as you are willing
to protect the new emperor

376
00:21:11,800 --> 00:21:13,770
with your life,

377
00:21:13,820 --> 00:21:15,420
the claim of the Marquis' rebellion

378
00:21:15,420 --> 00:21:16,710
will be debunked.

379
00:21:24,680 --> 00:21:25,230
Report.

380
00:21:25,790 --> 00:21:26,550
Your Highness,

381
00:21:26,550 --> 00:21:27,510
Grand Secretary.

382
00:21:27,510 --> 00:21:29,350
Ye Guangsheng, Marquis Changxing,
disobeyed orders

383
00:21:29,350 --> 00:21:30,960
and led 3,000 Black Armor
from the Capital Garrison

384
00:21:30,960 --> 00:21:31,920
to break into the palace

385
00:21:31,920 --> 00:21:32,790
to rebel.

386
00:21:34,160 --> 00:21:35,440
This is impossible.

387
00:21:38,680 --> 00:21:39,510
How is this possible?

388
00:21:39,510 --> 00:21:40,680
This is impossible.

389
00:21:40,790 --> 00:21:41,990
How is this possible?

390
00:21:45,640 --> 00:21:46,470
How dare you!

391
00:22:11,750 --> 00:22:13,690
Ye Xian risked
his life to save me.

392
00:22:13,750 --> 00:22:15,310
How dare you say the Marquis Changxing
is plotting a rebellion?

393
00:22:15,310 --> 00:22:16,830
That is absolute nonsense!

394
00:22:16,830 --> 00:22:17,510
Exactly.

395
00:22:18,160 --> 00:22:19,920
Even though that boy was just a double,

396
00:22:19,920 --> 00:22:21,750
I saw it clearly.

397
00:22:22,200 --> 00:22:22,880
Ye Xian

398
00:22:22,620 --> 00:22:24,190
[Empress Wu]

399
00:22:22,880 --> 00:22:25,610
risked his life, trying to
save the Crown Prince.

400
00:22:27,750 --> 00:22:28,640
Mr. Fu.

401
00:22:31,070 --> 00:22:32,200
Perhaps it's

402
00:22:32,880 --> 00:22:34,110
a misunderstanding.

403
00:22:34,960 --> 00:22:36,160
Marquis Changxing

404
00:22:37,310 --> 00:22:38,370
could not possibly

405
00:22:39,790 --> 00:22:40,590
rebel.

406
00:22:50,200 --> 00:22:51,070
Ye Xian!

407
00:22:52,920 --> 00:22:53,680
Save him now!

408
00:22:53,890 --> 00:22:54,830
Imperial Physicians!

409
00:22:54,830 --> 00:22:55,830
-Call the Imperial Physicians!
-Call the Imperial Physicians!

410
00:22:55,830 --> 00:22:58,160
-Call the Imperial Physicians!
-Ye Xian!

411
00:23:05,510 --> 00:23:06,160
My Lord.

412
00:23:06,670 --> 00:23:07,720
Father!

413
00:23:08,480 --> 00:23:09,590
-My Lord.
-Father!

414
00:23:09,720 --> 00:23:10,780
-My Lord.
-Father!

415
00:23:11,030 --> 00:23:11,550
Father!

416
00:23:12,110 --> 00:23:13,000
-My Lord!
-Father!

417
00:23:13,000 --> 00:23:13,720
My Lord!

418
00:23:13,790 --> 00:23:14,310
Father!

419
00:23:16,160 --> 00:23:16,880
Xian.

420
00:23:17,310 --> 00:23:19,010
I only suffered minor injuries.

421
00:23:19,010 --> 00:23:19,480
Madam.

422
00:23:19,640 --> 00:23:21,480
It is more urgent to treat

423
00:23:21,480 --> 00:23:22,870
the Marquis and Young Master Ye.

424
00:23:22,870 --> 00:23:23,350
Father.

425
00:23:23,350 --> 00:23:24,550
Quick, save them!

426
00:23:24,640 --> 00:23:25,890
Save them, quick!

427
00:23:25,910 --> 00:23:27,160
-What are you waiting for?
-Father!

428
00:23:27,160 --> 00:23:28,200
Help!

429
00:23:28,590 --> 00:23:30,350
-Father!
-My Lord.

430
00:23:30,370 --> 00:23:31,130
My Lord!

431
00:23:39,030 --> 00:23:40,830
The Marquis is very fortunate.

432
00:23:41,030 --> 00:23:43,420
That shot to the chest missed by an inch,

433
00:23:43,880 --> 00:23:45,640
and didn't damage his heart or lungs.

434
00:23:45,640 --> 00:23:48,170
The injury to his leg
is actually more severe.

435
00:23:48,200 --> 00:23:49,960
I will write two prescriptions.

436
00:23:49,960 --> 00:23:51,310
One to draw out the poison,

437
00:23:51,310 --> 00:23:52,880
and one to nourish the blood.

438
00:23:52,880 --> 00:23:54,820
If his fever breaks in three days,

439
00:23:55,030 --> 00:23:56,880
his life will be saved.

440
00:23:59,030 --> 00:24:00,560
Thank you for your trouble.

441
00:24:30,000 --> 00:24:33,140
[Immersed in the Classics and History]

442
00:24:33,480 --> 00:24:34,280
Third Master.

443
00:24:51,400 --> 00:24:52,460
At a time like this,

444
00:24:52,720 --> 00:24:54,380
you shouldn't have come to me.

445
00:24:54,550 --> 00:24:55,720
You did this,

446
00:24:56,200 --> 00:24:57,070
didn't you?

447
00:24:58,550 --> 00:25:00,590
Zhou Kuohai, Commander
of the Shenji Battalion,

448
00:25:00,590 --> 00:25:01,440
from the very beginning,

449
00:25:01,440 --> 00:25:02,900
has been Fu Hailian's man.

450
00:25:03,110 --> 00:25:04,640
Under Fu Hailian's orders,

451
00:25:04,750 --> 00:25:06,680
he intentionally injured my father,

452
00:25:06,680 --> 00:25:08,210
and framed him for treason.

453
00:25:08,590 --> 00:25:09,830
Using the Prince Ruichang's rebellion,

454
00:25:09,830 --> 00:25:11,350
the one who wanted to get rid of my father

455
00:25:11,350 --> 00:25:12,880
has always been Fu Hailian.

456
00:25:13,680 --> 00:25:14,400
And as

457
00:25:14,400 --> 00:25:15,920
Fu Hailian's top student,

458
00:25:16,350 --> 00:25:18,810
you couldn't have
been unaware of this plot.

459
00:25:21,880 --> 00:25:22,510
What?

460
00:25:23,590 --> 00:25:24,790
Speechless?

461
00:25:26,200 --> 00:25:27,860
If you really want me to speak,

462
00:25:28,350 --> 00:25:29,480
then I will.

463
00:25:30,350 --> 00:25:31,550
What do you think

464
00:25:31,680 --> 00:25:32,680
my relationship with

465
00:25:32,680 --> 00:25:33,830
your mansion is?

466
00:25:34,320 --> 00:25:35,350
What is the relationship

467
00:25:35,350 --> 00:25:36,810
between Fu Hailian and me?

468
00:25:38,030 --> 00:25:39,510
Do you apparently think

469
00:25:39,750 --> 00:25:40,680
that I must

470
00:25:40,750 --> 00:25:42,070
betray my mentor

471
00:25:42,160 --> 00:25:43,790
to help your mansion?

472
00:25:45,140 --> 00:25:46,590
Passing you the message

473
00:25:46,720 --> 00:25:48,270
and thinking of a way
to break the deadlock for you

474
00:25:48,270 --> 00:25:48,960
is already the absolute maximum

475
00:25:48,960 --> 00:25:50,030
I can do to help

476
00:25:50,110 --> 00:25:51,830
Marquis Changxing's Mansion.

477
00:25:51,830 --> 00:25:53,070
And as for these things,

478
00:25:53,070 --> 00:25:54,600
who was supposed to do them?

479
00:25:54,860 --> 00:25:55,750
As the only heir

480
00:25:55,750 --> 00:25:57,810
of the Marquis Changxing's Mansion,

481
00:25:58,240 --> 00:25:59,880
you spend your days playing around,

482
00:25:59,880 --> 00:26:01,270
ignorant and incompetent.

483
00:26:01,270 --> 00:26:02,110
Now that the Marquis Changxing's Mansion

484
00:26:02,110 --> 00:26:03,550
is on the verge of destruction,

485
00:26:03,550 --> 00:26:04,680
you can only seek help

486
00:26:04,680 --> 00:26:05,920
from an outsider like me.

487
00:26:05,920 --> 00:26:07,190
Why don't you reflect on

488
00:26:07,190 --> 00:26:08,250
your own problems?

489
00:26:08,510 --> 00:26:10,000
What kind of solution is yours?

490
00:26:10,000 --> 00:26:11,070
My father is severely injured

491
00:26:11,070 --> 00:26:11,720
and on the brink of death.

492
00:26:11,720 --> 00:26:13,920
At least the Marquis Changxing's Mansion
is still standing.

493
00:26:13,920 --> 00:26:15,450
The Marquis is still alive,

494
00:26:15,980 --> 00:26:17,070
and so are you.

495
00:26:32,350 --> 00:26:34,920
The Crown Prince
is about to ascend the throne.

496
00:26:34,920 --> 00:26:35,920
You had better

497
00:26:35,920 --> 00:26:37,450
go back and think carefully

498
00:26:38,240 --> 00:26:39,770
about what position to seek

499
00:26:40,160 --> 00:26:43,020
and how to revive
the Marquis Changxing's Mansion.

500
00:26:44,750 --> 00:26:45,350
Chen Yi,

501
00:26:46,000 --> 00:26:47,000
see the guest out.

502
00:26:57,350 --> 00:26:58,030
The entire street
of Prince Ruichang's Mansion

503
00:26:58,030 --> 00:26:59,480
has been blocked off.

504
00:27:00,030 --> 00:27:00,960
I even went over there today

505
00:27:00,960 --> 00:27:01,760
to take a look.

506
00:27:02,030 --> 00:27:02,790
Goodness.

507
00:27:02,920 --> 00:27:03,880
It was full of imperial guards,

508
00:27:03,880 --> 00:27:05,080
a massive dark crowd.

509
00:27:05,110 --> 00:27:06,460
You are really bold.

510
00:27:06,640 --> 00:27:08,770
I saw a lot of people going over to look.

511
00:27:08,880 --> 00:27:09,960
And I also heard

512
00:27:10,110 --> 00:27:12,590
that Prince Ruichang's
entire family will be executed.

513
00:27:12,590 --> 00:27:13,790
What do you mean
execute his entire family?

514
00:27:13,790 --> 00:27:16,500
Prince Ruichang is
the late emperor's own brother.

515
00:27:16,500 --> 00:27:18,280
[The Fragrant Brocade Pavilion]

516
00:27:16,880 --> 00:27:17,410
Who is it?

517
00:27:20,070 --> 00:27:20,880
It's me.

518
00:27:22,590 --> 00:27:23,520
Your Highness?

519
00:27:23,790 --> 00:27:24,880
Why are you here?

520
00:27:28,130 --> 00:27:31,250
[The Fragrant Brocade Pavilion]

521
00:27:32,200 --> 00:27:33,000
Zhao.

522
00:27:39,030 --> 00:27:39,640
Ye Xian.

523
00:27:47,080 --> 00:27:48,390
When I was young,

524
00:27:49,070 --> 00:27:50,270
I didn't like to talk,

525
00:27:51,110 --> 00:27:52,350
and I hated going out.

526
00:27:54,030 --> 00:27:55,890
My master would go to the mountain

527
00:27:56,350 --> 00:27:57,880
and catch leopard cats and baby hares

528
00:27:57,880 --> 00:27:58,940
for me to play with.

529
00:27:59,830 --> 00:28:01,690
He could also weave grasshoppers

530
00:28:01,750 --> 00:28:02,750
and dragonflies.

531
00:28:03,920 --> 00:28:05,200
In the summer,

532
00:28:06,070 --> 00:28:07,270
he picked hawthorns from the mountain

533
00:28:07,270 --> 00:28:09,130
to make candied hawthorns for me.

534
00:28:09,880 --> 00:28:11,880
He took me to the river to catch fish.

535
00:28:13,200 --> 00:28:14,350
The river crabs he found

536
00:28:14,350 --> 00:28:15,660
under the stones

537
00:28:15,920 --> 00:28:17,850
were only the size of a copper coin,

538
00:28:18,070 --> 00:28:19,800
but they were delicious fried.

539
00:28:22,550 --> 00:28:24,160
Once, I was bitten by a snake.

540
00:28:25,070 --> 00:28:26,270
He was very anxious.

541
00:28:27,240 --> 00:28:28,250
I had never seen him

542
00:28:28,250 --> 00:28:29,310
so anxious before.

543
00:28:30,400 --> 00:28:32,930
He sucked the poison out
for me with his mouth.

544
00:28:34,270 --> 00:28:36,130
But I killed him with my own hands.

545
00:29:12,900 --> 00:29:14,080
Let me ask you.

546
00:29:16,510 --> 00:29:17,880
Have you ever truly

547
00:29:19,680 --> 00:29:21,070
treated me as your disciple

548
00:29:21,070 --> 00:29:21,960
at all?

549
00:29:26,200 --> 00:29:27,640
For the last time,

550
00:29:30,790 --> 00:29:31,920
I will not

551
00:29:33,790 --> 00:29:34,720
lie to you.

552
00:29:47,440 --> 00:29:48,550
Actually,

553
00:29:52,030 --> 00:29:53,790
you have always been

554
00:29:56,920 --> 00:29:58,340
a pawn.

555
00:30:24,750 --> 00:30:26,010
Thinking about it now,

556
00:30:27,590 --> 00:30:29,070
his kindness to me

557
00:30:29,960 --> 00:30:31,200
was all for a purpose.

558
00:30:33,920 --> 00:30:35,000
He was afraid of losing

559
00:30:35,000 --> 00:30:36,350
my father's favor.

560
00:30:41,440 --> 00:30:42,960
And I was naive enough

561
00:30:45,960 --> 00:30:47,750
to think he was truly good to me.

562
00:31:02,270 --> 00:31:04,200
Thank you for helping me this time.

563
00:31:07,790 --> 00:31:09,450
Have a drink with me, will you?

564
00:31:10,610 --> 00:31:12,100
But you're injured.

565
00:31:12,440 --> 00:31:13,810
How can you drink?

566
00:31:14,680 --> 00:31:15,440
Then,

567
00:31:16,480 --> 00:31:17,200
you drink

568
00:31:18,030 --> 00:31:18,890
and I'll watch.

569
00:31:19,640 --> 00:31:21,500
It'll be like drinking it myself.

570
00:31:24,070 --> 00:31:24,680
Okay.

571
00:31:34,960 --> 00:31:35,750
Gu Jinzhao.

572
00:31:36,400 --> 00:31:37,030
Thank you.

573
00:31:38,000 --> 00:31:40,030
If you hadn't risked your life
to deliver the message,

574
00:31:40,030 --> 00:31:41,680
the Marquis Changxing's Mansion

575
00:31:41,680 --> 00:31:43,000
would be doomed by now.

576
00:31:43,920 --> 00:31:44,750
Gu Jinzhao.

577
00:31:45,240 --> 00:31:45,960
I thought

578
00:31:45,980 --> 00:31:47,840
that besides my blood relatives,

579
00:31:48,350 --> 00:31:49,070
no one else in this world

580
00:31:49,070 --> 00:31:50,670
would risk their life for me.

581
00:31:51,680 --> 00:31:52,480
Rest assured.

582
00:31:53,160 --> 00:31:55,690
Since you are willing
to risk your life for me,

583
00:31:55,750 --> 00:31:57,590
I will also repay you with mine.

584
00:32:00,260 --> 00:32:01,850
♪ Once I wrote of spring and fall ♪

585
00:32:02,650 --> 00:32:05,520
♪ Yet fell through time's abyss ♪

586
00:32:08,040 --> 00:32:09,160
♪ Every shade turned bitter ♪

587
00:32:10,070 --> 00:32:12,820
♪ Every longing became sorrow ♪

588
00:32:15,820 --> 00:32:16,920
♪ I've seen through right and wrong ♪

589
00:32:18,230 --> 00:32:21,250
♪ Old vows washed away like ash ♪

590
00:32:22,330 --> 00:32:28,590
♪ True devotion is knowing
the freedom within your heart♪

591
00:32:29,380 --> 00:32:32,290
♪ Word by word, hand in hand ♪

592
00:32:33,240 --> 00:32:35,970
♪ My heart grows cold like rust ♪

593
00:32:37,000 --> 00:32:40,000
♪ The stars send you far away ♪

594
00:32:40,840 --> 00:32:43,250
♪ Yet one thought still remains ♪

595
00:32:44,880 --> 00:32:47,660
♪ You share bright days with another ♪

596
00:32:48,650 --> 00:32:51,730
♪ I walk with my lonely shadow ♪

597
00:32:52,490 --> 00:33:01,760
♪ Filling every broken fold
with memories of us ♪

598
00:33:17,590 --> 00:33:20,750
By the grace of Heaven,
the Emperor proclaims:

599
00:33:20,950 --> 00:33:22,880
Fu Hailian is a pillar of the state.

600
00:33:22,880 --> 00:33:24,980
He is promoted
to Grand Secretary of the Zhongji Hall

601
00:33:24,980 --> 00:33:26,730
and Grand Preceptor of the Crown Prince.

602
00:33:26,730 --> 00:33:29,750
Vice Minister of the Crown Prince's
Household, Chen Yanyun,

603
00:33:29,750 --> 00:33:31,530
is promoted to
Left Vice Minister of Revenue

604
00:33:31,530 --> 00:33:33,810
and Grand Secretary
of the Eastern Cabinet.

605
00:33:33,810 --> 00:33:37,000
Marquis Changxing is rewarded
for his meritorious service to the throne

606
00:33:37,000 --> 00:33:38,920
with 300 taels of gold,

607
00:33:39,000 --> 00:33:40,510
3,000 notes of paper money,

608
00:33:40,510 --> 00:33:42,560
and 30 bolts of patterned silk.

609
00:33:42,730 --> 00:33:44,680
The heir of Marquis Changxing, Ye Xian,

610
00:33:44,680 --> 00:33:45,920
is rewarded for his meritorious service
in rescuing the Emperor

611
00:33:45,920 --> 00:33:47,760
with 100 taels of gold

612
00:33:47,790 --> 00:33:49,160
and 1,000 notes of paper money.

613
00:33:48,890 --> 00:33:50,730
[New Emperor, Shengde Emperor]

614
00:33:49,160 --> 00:33:50,880
He is also promoted
to the primary fifth rank

615
00:33:50,880 --> 00:33:52,590
as a Commander
of the Penal Court.

616
00:33:52,590 --> 00:33:54,680
Long live

617
00:33:54,790 --> 00:33:56,260
Your

618
00:33:56,510 --> 00:33:58,750
Majesty!

619
00:34:01,520 --> 00:34:05,210
[The Emperor Sets the Ultimate Principle]

620
00:34:10,380 --> 00:34:12,570
[Wenyuan Pavilion]

621
00:34:10,920 --> 00:34:12,320
You had His Majesty

622
00:34:12,340 --> 00:34:13,440
feign fainting while mourning,

623
00:34:13,440 --> 00:34:15,170
then switched in a substitute.

624
00:34:15,190 --> 00:34:16,040
That way,

625
00:34:16,230 --> 00:34:18,420
you made Prince Ruichang feel

626
00:34:18,510 --> 00:34:20,440
that His Majesty was still present,

627
00:34:20,440 --> 00:34:22,440
while also protecting His Majesty.

628
00:34:22,630 --> 00:34:24,150
What a masterstroke!

629
00:34:24,510 --> 00:34:26,600
I merely came up with the idea.

630
00:34:26,960 --> 00:34:28,290
The success of this plan

631
00:34:28,360 --> 00:34:31,360
relies entirely on His Majesty's
outstanding courage.

632
00:34:31,360 --> 00:34:33,030
Knowing full well
that a powerful enemy was near,

633
00:34:33,030 --> 00:34:34,480
he remained composed

634
00:34:35,480 --> 00:34:36,880
and used himself as bait.

635
00:34:37,000 --> 00:34:38,060
His Majesty is also

636
00:34:38,110 --> 00:34:40,110
trusting you more and more, Mentor.

637
00:34:40,190 --> 00:34:41,400
Wholeheartedly

638
00:34:41,510 --> 00:34:42,969
and without reservation.

639
00:34:45,909 --> 00:34:48,310
Marquis Changxing is severely injured.

640
00:34:49,630 --> 00:34:51,150
The returned imperial physician said

641
00:34:51,150 --> 00:34:53,280
he'll have to lie in bed for half a year.

642
00:34:54,630 --> 00:34:55,590
I doubt he'll ever

643
00:34:55,590 --> 00:34:57,360
be able to ride a horse again.

644
00:34:58,550 --> 00:35:01,280
At least the position
of commander of the Capital Garrison

645
00:35:01,280 --> 00:35:02,920
is now vacant.

646
00:35:05,110 --> 00:35:07,550
Marquis Changxing was lucky this time.

647
00:35:08,280 --> 00:35:09,690
Who would have thought Ye Xian

648
00:35:09,690 --> 00:35:10,750
would risk his life

649
00:35:11,000 --> 00:35:12,130
to save His Majesty?

650
00:35:12,880 --> 00:35:13,590
It shows

651
00:35:13,960 --> 00:35:15,440
he has extraordinary courage.

652
00:35:15,440 --> 00:35:18,230
That is exactly what I am worried about.

653
00:35:18,630 --> 00:35:19,880
Now His Majesty

654
00:35:20,000 --> 00:35:22,590
listens to Ye Xian

655
00:35:22,710 --> 00:35:24,070
and trusts him completely.

656
00:35:24,070 --> 00:35:25,920
Look, he wanted to join

657
00:35:26,880 --> 00:35:28,110
the Penal Court,

658
00:35:28,920 --> 00:35:31,670
and His Majesty immediately
made him a Commander.

659
00:35:31,670 --> 00:35:32,840
It must have been

660
00:35:33,440 --> 00:35:35,100
Ye Xian's own idea to go there.

661
00:35:35,280 --> 00:35:37,510
Feeling he couldn't go to the battlefield

662
00:35:37,510 --> 00:35:38,550
or achieve glory,

663
00:35:39,180 --> 00:35:41,340
he wanted to stay in the Penal Court.

664
00:35:43,760 --> 00:35:44,590
Actually, this played right

665
00:35:44,590 --> 00:35:46,480
into His Majesty's hands.

666
00:35:48,230 --> 00:35:49,440
Back then,

667
00:35:49,710 --> 00:35:52,240
the late Emperor established
the Penal Court

668
00:35:52,670 --> 00:35:56,280
to supervise officials independently
of the Three Judicial Offices.

669
00:35:56,280 --> 00:35:58,360
It answered only to the late Emperor,

670
00:35:59,320 --> 00:36:01,110
and had immense power.

671
00:36:01,960 --> 00:36:04,290
Later, the rebellion of Prince Chengqing

672
00:36:04,360 --> 00:36:05,960
implicated the Penal Court.

673
00:36:06,320 --> 00:36:08,980
The late Emperor intentionally
suppressed it,

674
00:36:09,400 --> 00:36:11,880
and it gradually lost power.

675
00:36:12,320 --> 00:36:13,580
This time, His Majesty

676
00:36:14,110 --> 00:36:16,400
sent Ye Xian to the Penal Court

677
00:36:16,510 --> 00:36:17,400
so

678
00:36:17,840 --> 00:36:19,070
he could

679
00:36:19,400 --> 00:36:20,550
take control of it

680
00:36:21,190 --> 00:36:23,150
on the Emperor's behalf,

681
00:36:24,000 --> 00:36:25,590
following the example of the late Emperor

682
00:36:25,590 --> 00:36:28,030
and restoring the Penal Court to power.

683
00:36:29,000 --> 00:36:30,730
Then, Mentor, what do you think

684
00:36:31,400 --> 00:36:32,230
of this?

685
00:36:38,550 --> 00:36:41,350
His Majesty wanting his own power

686
00:36:42,840 --> 00:36:44,070
is understandable.

687
00:36:46,230 --> 00:36:48,320
But the Commander of the Penal Court

688
00:36:48,320 --> 00:36:50,280
and the next Marquis Changxing

689
00:36:51,800 --> 00:36:54,000
must absolutely not be the same person.

690
00:36:58,230 --> 00:36:59,030
Therefore...

691
00:37:00,360 --> 00:37:01,070
Therefore,

692
00:37:01,550 --> 00:37:03,510
the title of Marquis Changxing

693
00:37:03,960 --> 00:37:05,490
can no longer be inherited.

694
00:37:08,580 --> 00:37:10,550
I understand.

695
00:37:14,150 --> 00:37:15,510
We need to take a long-term

696
00:37:15,510 --> 00:37:17,230
perspective on this matter.

697
00:37:17,440 --> 00:37:18,110
Look.

698
00:37:18,740 --> 00:37:21,140
The Marquis Changxing's Mansion just made

699
00:37:21,190 --> 00:37:23,150
a great contribution
in saving the Emperor.

700
00:37:23,150 --> 00:37:24,680
They are very powerful now.

701
00:37:25,360 --> 00:37:26,290
Don't make a move

702
00:37:27,110 --> 00:37:28,170
at this time.

703
00:37:29,840 --> 00:37:31,310
Just keep it in mind.

704
00:37:31,800 --> 00:37:32,230
Yes.

705
00:37:34,340 --> 00:37:35,150
By the way,

706
00:37:36,360 --> 00:37:38,110
my wife said the day before yesterday

707
00:37:38,110 --> 00:37:41,070
that she wanted to invite
the wives of the important officials

708
00:37:41,070 --> 00:37:42,230
over for a gathering.

709
00:37:42,230 --> 00:37:43,550
I just realized

710
00:37:44,230 --> 00:37:46,710
you are still single.

711
00:37:46,920 --> 00:37:48,610
It's my fault.

712
00:37:49,360 --> 00:37:51,920
I didn't think it through.

713
00:37:52,800 --> 00:37:54,700
You have joined the cabinet now.

714
00:37:54,760 --> 00:37:56,290
You can't be alone anymore.

715
00:37:56,760 --> 00:37:57,620
Someone must be

716
00:37:57,920 --> 00:37:59,650
by your side to take care of you.

717
00:38:02,030 --> 00:38:02,550
Well...

718
00:38:04,990 --> 00:38:07,620
[The Penal Court]

719
00:38:09,230 --> 00:38:09,840
My Lord.

720
00:38:10,480 --> 00:38:11,760
What is that smell?

721
00:38:13,760 --> 00:38:14,630
Young Master Ye

722
00:38:14,630 --> 00:38:15,960
found the dungeon's stench too strong,

723
00:38:15,960 --> 00:38:17,760
so he had incense lit all around.

724
00:38:19,000 --> 00:38:20,000
What does he think

725
00:38:20,000 --> 00:38:21,060
the Penal Court is?

726
00:38:21,280 --> 00:38:22,150
A brothel?

727
00:38:29,110 --> 00:38:30,030
Young Master Ye, if you

728
00:38:30,030 --> 00:38:30,920
can't even stand the smell

729
00:38:30,920 --> 00:38:31,880
of this dungeon,

730
00:38:32,440 --> 00:38:33,440
it only proves that you

731
00:38:33,440 --> 00:38:35,360
are not cut out for this line of work.

732
00:38:35,360 --> 00:38:37,000
You might as well report to His Majesty

733
00:38:37,000 --> 00:38:38,860
and leave this profession early.

734
00:38:40,510 --> 00:38:42,710
Commander Zhang, you just reminded me.

735
00:38:43,280 --> 00:38:44,360
From today on,

736
00:38:44,590 --> 00:38:45,440
move the interrogation room

737
00:38:45,440 --> 00:38:46,280
upstairs.

738
00:38:46,670 --> 00:38:47,150
You...

739
00:38:47,550 --> 00:38:49,080
I really don't like it here.

740
00:38:49,510 --> 00:38:50,960
There's not even a vent.

741
00:38:51,630 --> 00:38:53,160
But I like this line of work.

742
00:38:53,630 --> 00:38:55,030
I didn't think so before,

743
00:38:55,200 --> 00:38:56,780
but I suddenly realized

744
00:38:57,190 --> 00:38:58,850
this job is very educational.

745
00:38:58,960 --> 00:39:00,150
Educational?

746
00:39:01,510 --> 00:39:02,510
Did you know

747
00:39:02,670 --> 00:39:03,670
that human bones

748
00:39:03,840 --> 00:39:05,100
actually feel no pain?

749
00:39:05,440 --> 00:39:06,550
I just asked him.

750
00:39:07,190 --> 00:39:08,350
He said simply using a knife

751
00:39:08,350 --> 00:39:10,150
to scrape the bone doesn't hurt.

752
00:39:10,190 --> 00:39:12,030
It's the flesh that hurts.

753
00:39:14,670 --> 00:39:17,000
In the case of Prince Ruichang's treason,

754
00:39:17,110 --> 00:39:18,400
the principal offender
was already sentenced

755
00:39:18,400 --> 00:39:19,800
to be executed in autumn.

756
00:39:20,590 --> 00:39:22,700
Yet you had him sliced to death.

757
00:39:23,320 --> 00:39:24,610
Avenging a personal wrong
in the name of public interest,

758
00:39:24,610 --> 00:39:26,210
though understandable,

759
00:39:27,480 --> 00:39:28,150
still seems

760
00:39:28,150 --> 00:39:30,010
to go against the Emperor's will.

761
00:39:33,070 --> 00:39:35,070
Lord Zhang, you're quite eloquent.

762
00:39:35,960 --> 00:39:38,220
You're pinning two charges on me at once.

763
00:39:38,590 --> 00:39:40,070
But how do you know

764
00:39:40,280 --> 00:39:42,540
I wasn't acting under an imperial order?

765
00:39:42,630 --> 00:39:44,230
Where is the imperial order?

766
00:39:45,550 --> 00:39:47,550
If you don't believe me, Lord Zhang,

767
00:39:47,620 --> 00:39:49,420
I can take you to ask His Majesty.

768
00:39:54,020 --> 00:39:56,160
I was just joking.

769
00:39:57,110 --> 00:39:59,020
Young Master Ye, you're
deeply favored by His Majesty,

770
00:39:59,020 --> 00:40:00,250
as everyone knows.

771
00:40:00,590 --> 00:40:03,190
Naturally, you wouldn't
deceive the Emperor.

772
00:40:04,980 --> 00:40:06,740
I heard that you

773
00:40:07,150 --> 00:40:08,150
volunteered to raid the house of

774
00:40:08,150 --> 00:40:10,210
Yun Tao, Commander of the North City.

775
00:40:10,630 --> 00:40:12,120
If I remember correctly,

776
00:40:12,190 --> 00:40:14,840
I'm still in charge of this Penal Court.

777
00:40:15,840 --> 00:40:17,480
You didn't even inform me

778
00:40:17,630 --> 00:40:18,480
before asking His Majesty

779
00:40:18,480 --> 00:40:19,880
for this assignment.

780
00:40:20,360 --> 00:40:22,190
Isn't that a bit out of line?

781
00:40:24,400 --> 00:40:25,190
Out of line?

782
00:40:27,190 --> 00:40:28,480
Why don't I think so?

783
00:40:29,190 --> 00:40:30,630
You just said earlier

784
00:40:30,880 --> 00:40:32,880
that I'm avenging a personal wrong.

785
00:40:32,880 --> 00:40:34,530
Only by avenging a personal wrong

786
00:40:34,530 --> 00:40:36,050
can a raid be thorough.

787
00:40:36,360 --> 00:40:37,760
And only a thorough raid

788
00:40:38,280 --> 00:40:40,000
will please His Majesty, right?

789
00:40:40,000 --> 00:40:41,610
We all work for His Majesty.

790
00:40:41,670 --> 00:40:43,840
Don't be so petty, Lord Zhang.

791
00:40:44,550 --> 00:40:45,800
I even want to ask you

792
00:40:46,110 --> 00:40:47,400
for some good men.

793
00:40:51,480 --> 00:40:53,790
Then when do you plan to go?

794
00:40:55,110 --> 00:40:56,280
When?

795
00:40:56,550 --> 00:40:58,480
I really haven't thought about it.

796
00:40:59,150 --> 00:41:00,510
How about today?

797
00:41:00,670 --> 00:41:01,480
Today?

798
00:41:02,800 --> 00:41:03,800
It's a raid.

799
00:41:04,110 --> 00:41:04,800
Do we need to

800
00:41:04,800 --> 00:41:06,460
pick an auspicious day for it?

801
00:41:07,670 --> 00:41:08,190
Go.

802
00:41:08,800 --> 00:41:10,030
Gather the men

803
00:41:10,190 --> 00:41:10,990
and follow me.

804
00:41:12,070 --> 00:41:13,150
Yes, Commander Ye.

805
00:41:14,880 --> 00:41:15,880
Then, Lord Zhang,

806
00:41:16,130 --> 00:41:18,390
I'll go get busy.

807
00:41:23,110 --> 00:41:23,630
My Lord.

808
00:41:24,280 --> 00:41:25,510
His Majesty has just ascended the throne.

809
00:41:25,510 --> 00:41:26,340
Many real positions

810
00:41:26,340 --> 00:41:28,150
have been filled
with His Majesty's confidants.

811
00:41:28,150 --> 00:41:30,320
I'm afraid this Young Master Ye is also...

812
00:41:30,320 --> 00:41:32,480
He thinks he can replace me?

813
00:41:33,310 --> 00:41:35,620
It's still unknown who will win.

814
00:41:40,150 --> 00:41:41,320
At first,

815
00:41:41,410 --> 00:41:43,880
I thought people just visited
more often at the end of the year.

816
00:41:43,880 --> 00:41:45,320
Later, I found out

817
00:41:45,800 --> 00:41:48,070
that they were all
using visiting me as an excuse

818
00:41:48,070 --> 00:41:49,600
to play matchmaker for you.

819
00:41:50,290 --> 00:41:51,100
Look.

820
00:41:52,360 --> 00:41:55,110
This is Lord Gao's second daughter.

821
00:41:55,400 --> 00:41:57,780
This is Vice Minister Wang's
younger sister.

822
00:41:55,430 --> 00:41:56,680
[Respectfully submitted by Gao Zhongwen,
Minister of Ceremonial Affairs]

823
00:41:56,680 --> 00:41:57,110
[With deepest respect, Bai Chizheng,
Chancellor of the Imperial Academy]

824
00:41:57,130 --> 00:41:57,610
[To Madam Chen,
with respectful greetings]

825
00:41:58,320 --> 00:42:01,480
This is Chancellor Bai's eldest daughter.

826
00:42:02,440 --> 00:42:03,550
The three of them

827
00:42:04,190 --> 00:42:06,420
seem like a decent match for you.

828
00:42:07,230 --> 00:42:08,890
As for the rest girls

829
00:42:08,960 --> 00:42:11,440
from minor official or merchant families

830
00:42:11,590 --> 00:42:12,920
are not suitable.

831
00:42:13,630 --> 00:42:15,480
After all, your wife

832
00:42:15,760 --> 00:42:17,920
will be at least
a second-rank titled lady,

833
00:42:17,920 --> 00:42:19,550
and the wife of a Grand Secretary.

834
00:42:19,550 --> 00:42:21,000
In the future, she will have to

835
00:42:21,000 --> 00:42:23,030
handle social interactions for you.

836
00:42:23,030 --> 00:42:25,960
A woman from a humble family won't do.

837
00:42:40,960 --> 00:42:41,590
Chen Yi.

838
00:42:45,000 --> 00:42:45,800
Third Master.

839
00:42:47,470 --> 00:42:48,660
Go to the Gu family

840
00:42:49,360 --> 00:42:51,760
and ask if Miss Gu is available.

841
00:42:53,070 --> 00:42:53,800
Yes, My Lord.

842
00:43:09,180 --> 00:43:11,490
[Baoxiang Temple]

843
00:43:36,520 --> 00:43:40,090
[A Splendid Match]
